### Create product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reference": "REF-001",
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "description": "A test product",
  "unitPrice": 19.99,
  "category": "General",
  "currentStock": 100,
  "reorderPoint": 10,
  "unitOfMeasure": "pcs"
}

### List all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products

### Get product by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/{id}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reference": "REF-001-UPDATED",
  "name": "Sample Product Updated",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "unitPrice": 24.99,
  "category": "UpdatedCategory",
  "currentStock": 80,
  "reorderPoint": 5,
  "unitOfMeasure": "pcs"
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/{id}

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/ByCategory/{category}

### Get products by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/ByName/{name}

### Get products by reference
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/ByReference/{reference}

